additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Water, Sodium Carbonate, Anionic and Nonionic Surfactants*, Sodium Citrate*, Soap*, Optical Brightener, Sequesterants, Fragrance and Preservatives. *Plant Derived.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Use only as directed. If swallowed, rinse mouth out and drink 2 glasses of water to dilute and seek medical advice. If eye contact occurs, rinse eye thoroughly with water. Seek medical advice. For medical advice call Poisons Information Centre 131 126.

description: This plant based formula easily cuts through dirt, leaving laundry clean, fresh & cuddly.Plus it isn't just for baby: it's also perfect for the entire family, especially those with sensitive skin.
